cc:Work.dc:description: A CD stand to display CDs on a counter top, etc.

text.tspan: Download Gnu Linux directly online, or contact

flowRoot.flowPara: This stand is part of Software Freedom Day. SFD works to promote software freedom in all aspects of society.
The software on these discs is made by an international community of thousands of developers who are independent of any single organisation.
This software comes with no guarantee. See information on disc for more details.
